    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Khorus, a once-thriving world ruled by the Lyramancers, wielders of music-magic, now a decaying land that has lain silent for 1,000 years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a bard, given the gift of Lyramancy, who must use their powers to defeat the malevolent god of silence and restore harmony to Khorus.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rhythmic Combat:</strong> Hack and slash wielding a variety of instruments, roll to avoid damage, or play a quick note to parry incoming attacks. Boost damage by chaining <strong>rhythmic combos</strong> with perfectly timed attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/c76007d0abd03286f3a84395e49a6b74.poster.avif?t=1751930474\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/c76007d0abd03286f3a84395e49a6b74.webm?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/c76007d0abd03286f3a84395e49a6b74.mp4?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/a5f53270f94242f001e0d18ee0bdf02c.poster.avif?t=1751930474\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/a5f53270f94242f001e0d18ee0bdf02c.webm?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/a5f53270f94242f001e0d18ee0bdf02c.mp4?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lyramancy:</strong> Play songs that conjure powerful magic, release the spirits of fallen foes, or unlock secrets waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/a853af4cc2969377d5bab1e584b9347a.poster.avif?t=1751930474\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/a853af4cc2969377d5bab1e584b9347a.webm?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/a853af4cc2969377d5bab1e584b9347a.mp4?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Boss Battles:</strong> Bosses provide intense trials and satisfying rewards. Defeating them will get you ever closer to the god of silence that now holds power over Khorus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/7655a11b00f54ee363d3546629bbb3c2.poster.avif?t=1751930474\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/7655a11b00f54ee363d3546629bbb3c2.webm?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/7655a11b00f54ee363d3546629bbb3c2.mp4?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration:</strong> Run, jump, and climb with precise control to explore a beautiful handcrafted world. Acquire instruments and abilities that open up new pathways and secrets to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/11653dee8f2de52013b50700b2c4a758.poster.avif?t=1751930474\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/11653dee8f2de52013b50700b2c4a758.webm?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/11653dee8f2de52013b50700b2c4a758.mp4?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customization:</strong> Collect items, instruments, and equipment with a variety of stat bonuses and upgrades. Mix and match different sets to suit your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/3e00b62eca614c494b4cd61eb367150a.poster.avif?t=1751930474\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/3e00b62eca614c494b4cd61eb367150a.webm?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/3e00b62eca614c494b4cd61eb367150a.mp4?t=1751930474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
